{"tid":1832201,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港大醫學院推算武漢可能有約1300多宗肺炎確診病例","createTime":"2020-01-21T04:05:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-21T07:11:08.000Z","uid":212626,"like":157,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"0a9d580a629bce01529c1986fc1fb29c1f011dfe","tid":1832201,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T04:05:21.000Z","msg":"港大醫學院世衞傳染病流行病學及控制合作中心發表有關內地新型冠狀病毒肺炎個案的最近情況，根據現有數據，推算武漢可能有約1300多宗確診病例。<br />\n<br />\n中心創立總監梁卓偉表示，利用數學模型研究，<span style=\"color: red;\">推算截止本月17日為止，武漢最有可能約有1300多宗個案，若平均估計則有約1680宗個案</span>。他認為有關推算，與早前倫敦帝國學院流行病學專家的推算，指武漢可能有超過1700宗確診病例的說法，互相引證。<br />\n<br />\n梁卓偉表示，以有關模型推算，香港現時有確診個案的上限為3個，但最佳估算為沒有個案，因此香港暫未有進口個案，屬意料中事。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1503926-20200121.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1503926-20200121.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=DnofPF37Lcb9g14kkk4r6gbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=38f3c237\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1503926-20200121.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=2e2600a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1503926-20200121.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"e4fa13c59dee8c70360cbb52f39b14f9439d85cd","tid":1832201,"uid":67294,"like":14,"dislike":13,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T04:06:45.000Z","msg":"Dllm抄bbc我都識up啦"},{"pid":"791fa8603e3c8e1d232a1cd4164d281fc98aa6f9","tid":1832201,"uid":22329,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T04:07:12.000Z","msg":"Live緊"},{"pid":"11c98de7623b1efcf1cfb113f7d797a6309edff9","tid":1832201,"uid":49456,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T04:07:49.000Z","msg":"咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cec0032b5dc4eea7a58a67504f05ff08b25d778","tid":1832201,"uid":14918,"like":35,"dislike":2,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T0